<i>just say, "Why wouldn't </i>
<i>I use this? It's too easy".</i>

33:05.316 --> 33:06.609
[somber music playing]

33:10.905 --> 33:14.617
<i>The most disturbing thing</i>
<i>about my involvement</i>
<i>in drones</i>

