33:47.191 --> 33:48.484
<i>I mean, does that happen?</i>

33:49.485 --> 33:50.528
<i>How do we know?</i>

33:50.862 --> 33:53.990
<i>How is it possible to know </i>
<i>who ends up living or dying?</i>

33:59.954 --> 34:02.874
[woman] So, folks, welcome
to the Commonwealth Club.

34:02.957 --> 34:05.001
We have the great
privilege tonight

34:05.084 --> 34:08.295
to have a chance to talk
with General
Stanley McChrystal,

34:08.670 --> 34:13.467
who had a very distinguished
34-year career
in the American military.

34:13.760 --> 34:15.678
His last assignment

34:15.762 --> 34:19.098
was as the commander
of the International
Security Assistance Force,

34:19.389 --> 34:20.766
in Afghanistan.

34:21.225 --> 34:23.143
Won't you
Commonwealth Club members

34:23.226 --> 34:25.103
join me in welcoming
Stan McChrystal.

34:30.735 --> 34:32.027
[Stan] Think about
today's world.

34:32.445 --> 34:35.697
You can get information
from everywhere in real time.

34:35.782 --> 34:37.867
You can talk to anyone
in your organization.

34:37.949 --> 34:40.328
In my Situational Awareness
Room where we called it,

34:40.411 --> 34:42.288
we had about 12 screens
on the wall.

34:42.496 --> 34:45.541
And they were all showing
operations in real time,

34:46.042 --> 34:47.418
full motion video,
we called it.

34:47.502 --> 34:49.420
Like the live TV
from Predator

34:49.629 --> 34:51.089
unmanned aerial vehicles
above them.

34:51.172 --> 34:53.591
So, we could watch
every one of our operators,

34:53.674 --> 34:55.259
landing a helicopter,
get out of a vehicle,

34:55.342 --> 34:56.260
move on the target.

34:56.552 --> 34:59.722
And because of a system
we set up that went through
our secure Internet,

35:00.014 --> 35:02.350
we could hear
every radio transmission

35:02.725 --> 35:05.520
and if I was sitting
in Baghdad, I could hear
radio transmissions

35:05.603 --> 35:06.687
from a raid
in Afghanistan.

35:07.522 --> 35:08.481
And if I wanted to,

35:08.564 --> 35:12.610
I could reach down and talk
to Sergeant X, on the ground,

35:13.528 --> 35:15.196
on an objective in Afghanistan.

35:15.738 --> 35:19.450
Now, I never did that
but the technology now
allows you to do that.

35:19.992 --> 35:22.245
So, the first thing
to understand is that,
that's deceptive.

35:23.079 --> 35:26.415
It's seductive and deceptive,
because, if you see things
in two dimension

35:26.499 --> 35:29.544
you get the opinion that
you're at 10,000 feet,
you see this photograph,

35:29.669 --> 35:31.379
you know what's going on.

35:31.671 --> 35:32.630
You don't know
what's going on,

35:32.713 --> 35:34.465
You know what you see
in two dimensions.

35:34.757 --> 35:36.175
[indistinct chatter]

35:44.100 --> 35:45.017
Lisa, L-I-S-A?

35:45.268 --> 35:46.185
Yup.

35:48.354 --> 35:49.856
And... I'm...

35:50.857 --> 35:52.191
Go on with
the question, please.

35:52.441 --> 35:55.903
Okay, so, I'm very curious,
I understand that you're...

35:56.362 --> 35:58.281
a little weary about
the drone program,

35:58.364 --> 36:00.658
-Uh-huh.
-and I'm wondering,
what your...

36:02.034 --> 36:03.452
views of the program are.

36:03.619 --> 36:06.622
Yeah, I think drones
are here to stay,
and they're necessary.

36:07.081 --> 36:10.251
But you have to understand
how people perceive things.

36:10.334 --> 36:13.421
So, it's one thing
to do things,
but it's another

36:13.546 --> 36:15.548
to anger a population
in the process.

36:15.965 --> 36:18.885
So, I think you got to make
that value decision,
you gotta say...

36:19.093 --> 36:21.929
In each case you gotta
make the decision,
"Is it worth it?"

36:22.430 --> 36:24.140
Because, you are gonna create,

36:24.557 --> 36:26.642
you know, some ill-will
in the process.

36:26.851 --> 36:29.187
I also think we need
to explain it
to the world better.

36:30.521 --> 36:33.524
But again, I'm not one
of those people who thinks
it's not gonna be around.

36:33.608 --> 36:35.318
-I mean, technology
doesn't go back.
-Oh, no. It doesn't.

36:35.401 --> 36:37.320
Yeah, once it's out
of the bag,
it's out of the bag.

36:37.445 --> 36:39.780
And it's not immoral or moral,

36:40.281 --> 36:43.159
but it has to be understood
and it has to be described
to people.

36:43.242 --> 36:44.702
It has to be
very carefully used.

36:44.994 --> 36:47.038
I just think
it's that important.

36:47.496 --> 36:49.540
Well, I just wanna say,
thank you.
